Thapelo Edwin Moshele Multimedia &nbsp; &nbsp; User Galleries &nbsp; &nbsp; News in Pictures Send us your pictures &nbsp; &nbsp; Send us your stories The Roodepan police is appealing to the community to assist them in finding a 25 year old man who was reported missing on 28 December 2016. Thapelo Edwin Moshele was last seen wearing a black jean, green T-shirt and brown shoes before he was reported missing.According to the police description, Moshele is 1,65 m tall, has black hair and is dark in complexion.Anyone who might have information about his whereabouts is requested to contact Sgt Janine Anthony of the Roodepan police station on 063-818-7166. All information will be treated as confidential.24.com encourages commentary submitted via MyNews24. Contributions of 200 words or more will be considered for publication.